# 🧠 Smart AI Recruitment System

An intelligent recruitment platform that automates resume screening using **Machine Learning and NLP**.

This system helps recruiters quickly identify the best candidates by analyzing resumes and matching them with job descriptions using AI.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👤 User Roles
- Admin
- Recruiter
- Candidate

### 📄 Resume Processing
- Upload PDF resumes
- Automatic text extraction
- Skill extraction using NLP

### 🤖 AI Resume Scoring
- TF-IDF similarity
- BERT semantic matching
- Final score calculation

### 🏆 Candidate Ranking
- Candidates ranked by AI match score
- Top candidates automatically shortlisted

### 📊 Admin Analytics Dashboard
- Total users
- Total jobs
- Applications
- Shortlisted candidates
- Interactive charts (Chart.js)

### 💡 AI Job Recommendations
- Suggests jobs based on candidate skills

### 📈 Resume Skill Visualization
- Skill distribution analysis
- Graph-based visualization

### 📧 Email OTP Authentication
- Secure login with OTP verification

---

## 🏗️ System Architecture
Frontend (HTML / CSS / JS)
│
▼
Flask Backend (Auth, Jobs, Dashboard)
│
▼
FastAPI AI Service (Resume Scoring)
│
▼
PostgreSQL / SQLite Database

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

### Backend
- Flask
- FastAPI
- SQLAlchemy
- Flask-JWT
- Flask-Mail

### AI / NLP
- Sentence Transformers (BERT)
- Scikit-learn
- TF-IDF Vectorization

### Frontend
- HTML
- CSS (Glassmorphism UI)
- JavaScript
- Chart.js

### Database
- SQLite (development)
- PostgreSQL (production)

